{"id": "1520431120238252124", "channel_id": "1520431120238252124", "author_id": "614083839131648021", "author_name": "shostakovich524", "content": "現在推出的幾位喚醒體原有四色上做了點改動(三回合cd)的新界域。(沒記錯的話，徐後面的都是新界域，墨菲我忘了什麼時候出的了)\n\n那麼我有一個問題，後續會出現的喚醒體是不是就不會是原來的四色，而是有三回合cd的新界域？換句話說，會有純<:realm_aequor:1437283645051375777>/<:realm_caro:1437283648134058004>/<:realm_chaos:1437283650809888768>/<:realm_ultra:1437283545784651926>界域的新喚醒體嗎？還是仍然會是晦暝·深海/繁育·血肉/？？·混沌/奇點·超維？\n\n決定一個喚醒體在舊界域還是新界域的因素是什麼？是版本？還是角色本身的機制？🧐", "timestamp": "2026-06-27T14:10:27.309000+00:00", "thread_id": "1520431120238252124", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-27T14:13:15.177000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}]}
{"id": "1520404258539835492", "channel_id": "1520404258539835492", "author_id": "153267826755502081", "author_name": "violet.raven", "content": "Hello BIAV team! \n\nFor the longest of time i noticed tawil had two canvas grey cutouts in her underhair on both sides of her neck plus what is most likely a fill tool error near her eyelashes. (could be makeup?) - picture 1\nI have noticed this in most places where her standard model is used. \n\nFurthermore, it is present in some of her avatars but not all so it is not necessarily consistent. I assumed because of that, that it is a mistake as, if it was part of the hair it misses hair texture and if it were part of her veil the material texture. - picture 2 has the grey while picture 3 doesn’t.\n\nIn another case, specifically her event splash art, the gray is actually incorporated into her hair beautifully as actual underhair pattern -picture 4, while in the story it is instead removed (likely an artistic choice in this case) - picture 5.\n\nThat specific grey is also not present in her battle chibi - picture 6. \n\nOverall i wanted to bring some attention to this as she is my most beloved awakener. I would like to know at least if this is an intended part of her design, or possibly get it fixed/updated in the future if it isn’t.\n\nThank you for the answer in anticipation. Keep up the good work BIAV <:celeste_wish:1333977832791085107>", "timestamp": "2026-06-27T12:23:42.981000+00:00", "thread_id": "1520404258539835492", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-27T12:28:25.817000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "Horla_shy", "emoji_id": "1468259514091573350", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "💀", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1520404258904608910", "filename": "IMG_8918.png", "content_type": "video/quicktime", "size": 137159, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1520404258539835492/1520404258904608910/IMG_8918.png?ex=6a41124f&is=6a3fc0cf&hm=50a32358fc8419dc23a57f4eb9c7075ca3cdff87c179dd37c7bb94ea36cfbe87&"}, {"id": "1520404259227697354", "filename": "IMG_8916.png", "content_type": "video/quicktime", "size": 148643, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1520404258539835492/1520404259227697354/IMG_8916.png?ex=6a41124f&is=6a3fc0cf&hm=4315f3b8a65bdb7babe90360608a5d99b7f0492cb2261e947da5f77133c7f865&"}, {"id": "1520404259743731712", "filename": "IMG_8917.png", "content_type": "video/quicktime", "size": 429121, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1520404258539835492/1520404259743731712/IMG_8917.png?ex=6a41124f&is=6a3fc0cf&hm=7d9236d3defb42f6468fd5a229492cf7d1f58a44af9c3b31e7aa8e689ad729a1&"}, {"id": "1520404260091596861", "filename": "IMG_8919.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 87971, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1520404258539835492/1520404260091596861/IMG_8919.jpg?ex=6a41124f&is=6a3fc0cf&hm=6cd28906eb17b0cb978ae2355539c828deb1c2f23a07c7ec1a4ee10a3d0d1c20&"}, {"id": "1520404260502765598", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "video/quicktime", "size": 591124, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1520404258539835492/1520404260502765598/image.png?ex=6a41124f&is=6a3fc0cf&hm=8a0f6efc2f4d45c8696c946c4f508a91eba7e015b774ad8ed3c22580312191e3&"}, {"id": "1520404260800696320", "filename": "IMG_8920.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 38503, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1520404258539835492/1520404260800696320/IMG_8920.png?ex=6a41124f&is=6a3fc0cf&hm=c67e44583e0b0fcd3e0400c5acf096c04cc514e15eef666a9195fe591c6b5088&"}]}
